WEBVTT

00:06.541 --> 00:08.164
So how's life as an empty nester?

00:08.188 --> 00:11.586
Oh, I miss Nicky a lot.

00:11.586 --> 00:13.831
Remember the first time
Nicky went away without us?

00:13.855 --> 00:15.617
Dance camp.

00:15.641 --> 00:17.610
You did not ask to meet

00:17.634 --> 00:20.235
to walk down memory lane, did you?

00:20.595 --> 00:24.074
Um, I, uh, I joined a charity

00:24.098 --> 00:27.177
that takes on innocence cases.

00:27.201 --> 00:28.545
Okay.

00:28.569 --> 00:31.715
And I'm representing a client
that's been in prison

00:31.739 --> 00:36.053
for five years, uh, and, uh,
Erin, he didn't do it.

00:36.077 --> 00:38.289
He tell you that?

00:38.313 --> 00:40.291
He was put away for murder

00:40.315 --> 00:42.426
based largely on an eyewitness account,

00:42.450 --> 00:44.395
and the witness recanted,

00:44.419 --> 00:47.331
and the, uh, the detective
who handled the case, um,

00:47.355 --> 00:51.502
let's just say this wasn't his
first questionable conviction.

00:51.526 --> 00:53.837
Well, doesn't sound like a slam dunk.

00:53.861 --> 00:56.106
Trust me, this kid was railroaded.

00:56.457 --> 00:57.958
Kid?

00:59.667 --> 01:02.579
Yeah, he was 20 when
he went into the system.

01:03.547 --> 01:05.849
Okay, so why are you coming to me?

01:06.842 --> 01:09.309
Because you're the one who put him away.

01:15.049 --> 01:17.861
- Leave him alone, yo.
- This yours?

01:17.885 --> 01:20.197
I asked you a question. Is this yours?

01:20.221 --> 01:21.765
No! Why don't y'all get out of here.

01:21.789 --> 01:22.967
Y'all should leave me be.

01:22.991 --> 01:24.969
- Hey, back it up.
- Yo, everybody, stay back!

01:24.993 --> 01:27.538
Look, all right,
we're not gonna bring you in.

01:27.562 --> 01:29.473
It's a summons instead.

01:29.497 --> 01:31.775
- A summons?
- Take this ticket, all right?

01:34.202 --> 01:35.279
That's what you get!

01:43.211 --> 01:44.888
Yo, let's just go to the car.

01:44.912 --> 01:46.890
All right?

01:46.914 --> 01:49.259
<i>And the officers did nothing?</i>

01:49.283 --> 01:51.695
That's right,
put their tail between their legs

01:51.719 --> 01:53.230
and got into their patrol car.

01:54.097 --> 01:56.267
They both got less than
a year on the job.

01:56.291 --> 01:58.902
- That's no excuse.
- No, it's just a fact, boss.

01:58.926 --> 02:01.382
We don't teach our officers
not to fight back.

02:01.406 --> 02:02.818
We're not teaching them that, boss,

02:02.842 --> 02:04.471
but it's open season on cops.

02:04.472 --> 02:06.971
They should've arrested the guy
on the spot.

02:06.995 --> 02:09.854
I agree with you, boss, but you
got the media and politicians

02:09.877 --> 02:11.389
hammering them every day

02:11.413 --> 02:12.957
with anti-cop stuff.

02:12.981 --> 02:14.058
It has an effect.

02:14.082 --> 02:15.927
And anyone complicit needs to be found,

02:15.951 --> 02:19.012
arrested, and charged with
everything we can throw at them.

02:19.036 --> 02:21.032
We can put out a Finest Message
to the troops.

02:21.056 --> 02:22.533
No, call a press conference.

02:22.557 --> 02:24.001
I'll write something up.

02:24.544 --> 02:26.560
I know what needs to be said.

02:32.302 --> 02:33.945
Hey, you headed home?

02:33.969 --> 02:36.013
Did you hear what happened
to DeNoon and Malone?

02:36.037 --> 02:38.015
Yeah, I just saw that
on my phone. They okay?

02:38.039 --> 02:39.717
No, they came back humiliated.

02:39.741 --> 02:42.386
- Who did it?
- C.O. put up a screen grab of the perp.

02:42.410 --> 02:43.754
The guy wasn't arrested?

02:43.778 --> 02:45.122
No, they did nothing.

02:45.146 --> 02:47.491
They just got in their RMP and left.

02:48.986 --> 02:50.127
<i>What do we got?</i>

02:50.151 --> 02:53.117
Miriam Harton, 85 years old,
was assaulted and robbed

02:53.161 --> 02:56.234
in the vestibule as she entered
the building with groceries.

02:56.258 --> 02:57.468
Perp came up from behind her,

02:57.492 --> 02:59.103
pushed her to the ground and stomped her.

02:59.127 --> 03:00.605
- Any witnesses?
- I wish.

03:00.629 --> 03:02.773
Looks like she may have broken
a hip and maybe some ribs.

03:02.797 --> 03:04.584
We should check to see
if there are any cameras...

03:04.608 --> 03:06.577
No, I-I already asked.
Super's working on it.

03:06.601 --> 03:08.379
My partner and I already
started a canvass.

03:08.403 --> 03:09.614
Mrs. Harton.

03:09.638 --> 03:12.250
Detective Reagan,
my partner Detective Baez.

03:12.274 --> 03:14.852
Could you tell us about
the person who assaulted you?

03:14.876 --> 03:17.154
He... I thought he wanted to help.

03:17.178 --> 03:19.023
He opened the door for me,

03:19.047 --> 03:21.792
and then when I turned around, he hit me.

03:21.816 --> 03:23.394
It was a he, ma'am?

03:23.418 --> 03:25.943
My husband will be worried about me.

03:25.967 --> 03:28.065
Ma'am, it's really important
that you give us a description

03:28.089 --> 03:29.433
of the man who attacked you. Could you?

03:29.457 --> 03:31.872
My husband, my husband is waiting for me

03:31.896 --> 03:33.771
to come home with the groceries.

03:33.795 --> 03:36.107
- We need to get her checked out.
- Go ahead.

03:36.131 --> 03:38.976
Waiting for me.

03:41.336 --> 03:43.648
Hey. I want to talk to you.

03:43.672 --> 03:46.017
Hey, bro, hey, hey, bro,
I didn't do nothing, all right?

03:46.041 --> 03:47.942
You throw water on two police
officers earlier today?

03:47.966 --> 03:49.553
Hey, come on, man, throwing water

03:49.577 --> 03:51.668
ain't no crime. I ain't shoot nobody.

03:51.692 --> 03:53.596
- I'm talking to you.
- Man, all right, so what?

03:53.620 --> 03:55.226
Hey, you're under arrest.

03:56.069 --> 03:58.362
Man, you can't arrest me
for throwing water on no scum!

03:58.847 --> 04:00.665
It's just water, my dude. Yo...

04:04.759 --> 04:07.655
What the hell do you think
you're doing, you stupid dick?!

04:07.679 --> 04:10.374
It's just water, right?
Hands behind your back.

04:10.398 --> 04:12.310
Hey, bro, what?! Come on, man.

04:14.336 --> 04:16.079
- Yo, let him go!
- No, he got rights!

04:16.103 --> 04:17.515
What you taking him away for?

